  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🛠️MANAGE YOUR FACTORY🛠️</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/8ce050bc5dcb880c1ac3f2445b6d2db2.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/8ce050bc5dcb880c1ac3f2445b6d2db2.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/8ce050bc5dcb880c1ac3f2445b6d2db2.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy your resources, storage canisters, conveyors, and specific machines, and start manufacturing deadly goods. Expand your factory, unlock new weapons to craft, and new machines to build, and become a lord of war. You can customize and expand your factory to your desire.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔎CATCH IMPOSTORS🔍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/6ae943c2c98917f6ccbca1ab03cc2d81.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/6ae943c2c98917f6ccbca1ab03cc2d81.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/6ae943c2c98917f6ccbca1ab03cc2d81.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everyone is suitable to purchasing a firearm, that's a bummer. You have to check customers' ID to see if the fit this criteria and send them home empty-handed. If you sell to an impostor, well, you'll get punished.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏪MANAGE YOUR SHOP🏪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/bac27488d6901577d0d1665ab3096996.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/bac27488d6901577d0d1665ab3096996.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/bac27488d6901577d0d1665ab3096996.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the biggest gun shop ever. Interact with different types of customers, get special orders from around the world, sell rockets, pistols, rifles, and your own customized weapons, get rich, and expand your gun manufacturing kingdom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✅UPGRADE YOUR MACHINES✅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/1dd113990a6290b92196f12b4a5ff4fb.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/1dd113990a6290b92196f12b4a5ff4fb.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/1dd113990a6290b92196f12b4a5ff4fb.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade the abilities of your machines, make them faster, and more profitable. Unlock, and obtain machine modules with special attributes. Install them to your machines and make them work with unique effects and attributes. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👷‍♂️HIRE WORKERS AND MANAGERS👨‍💼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of doing stuff someone else can do? Hire workers to do the dirty job for you. Hire managers to access special effects like increasing your customer rate, auto producing your guns or increasing the speed of your machines.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔫UNLOCK NEW WEAPONS AND MACHINES🔫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game,  you can buy licences to manufacture new and deadlier weapons. You can unlock new machines to complete your mass production orders and stock up your high quality gun store.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🛠️MANAGE YOUR FACTORY🛠️</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/8ce050bc5dcb880c1ac3f2445b6d2db2.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/8ce050bc5dcb880c1ac3f2445b6d2db2.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/8ce050bc5dcb880c1ac3f2445b6d2db2.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy your resources, storage canisters, conveyors, and specific machines, and start manufacturing deadly goods. Expand your factory, unlock new weapons to craft, and new machines to build, and become a lord of war. You can customize and expand your factory to your desire.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔎CATCH IMPOSTORS🔍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/6ae943c2c98917f6ccbca1ab03cc2d81.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/6ae943c2c98917f6ccbca1ab03cc2d81.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/6ae943c2c98917f6ccbca1ab03cc2d81.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everyone is suitable to purchasing a firearm, that's a bummer. You have to check customers' ID to see if the fit this criteria and send them home empty-handed. If you sell to an impostor, well, you'll get punished.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏪MANAGE YOUR SHOP🏪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/bac27488d6901577d0d1665ab3096996.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/bac27488d6901577d0d1665ab3096996.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/bac27488d6901577d0d1665ab3096996.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the biggest gun shop ever. Interact with different types of customers, get special orders from around the world, sell rockets, pistols, rifles, and your own customized weapons, get rich, and expand your gun manufacturing kingdom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✅UPGRADE YOUR MACHINES✅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/1dd113990a6290b92196f12b4a5ff4fb.poster.avif?t=1754338780\" width=600 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/1dd113990a6290b92196f12b4a5ff4fb.webm?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137520/extras/1dd113990a6290b92196f12b4a5ff4fb.mp4?t=1754338780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade the abilities of your machines, make them faster, and more profitable. Unlock, and obtain machine modules with special attributes. Install them to your machines and make them work with unique effects and attributes. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👷‍♂️HIRE WORKERS AND MANAGERS👨‍💼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tired of doing stuff someone else can do? Hire workers to do the dirty job for you. Hire managers to access special effects like increasing your customer rate, auto producing your guns or increasing the speed of your machines.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔫UNLOCK NEW WEAPONS AND MACHINES🔫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the game,  you can buy licences to manufacture new and deadlier weapons. You can unlock new machines to complete your mass production orders and stock up your high quality gun store.</p>",
